<TEXT>
<P>
The San Pedro Eastview All-Stars play the Alaska state champion Monday in a 
first-round game of the Western Regional Little League Tournament at Al 
Houghton Park in San Bernardino. Game time is 8 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
The champion of the Western Regional advances to the Little League World Series 
in Williamsport, Pa. Eastview advanced to regional play by winning the Southern 
California Tournament last week. Eastview, which went unbeaten in the 
tournament, defeated Plaza Little League of Long Beach, 17-7, in the title game 
at Culver City Park. 
</P>
