<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A top East German sports journalist has defected to the West by ferry after 
covering a track meet in Malmo, Sweden. Joerg Kotterba, 39, wrote for the daily 
Berlin Zeitung and edited the weekly Der Leichtathlet (The Athlete). 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
