<HEADLINE>
<P>
ILLEGAL ALIENS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding your Aug. 6 editorial ("Keep Open a Window to Police"): "detaining 
illegal aliens who had committed no crime"? 
</P>
<P>
The last time I looked, it was a crime to enter this country without permission 
and proper papers. This is why those who enter without permission are called 
illegal aliens -- they are here illegally, having broken federal law in the 
process. 
</P>
<P>
DUNCAN McCARTHY 
</P>
<P>
San Diego 
